Functional requirements describe what the system must do. Each requirement ensures the system meets user needs.

Functional Requirements

FR-01: User Login
System must allow secure login for authorized users.

FR-02: Add Stock
Users can add new stock details.

FR-03: Update Stock
Users can modify stock quantities.

FR-04: Track Inventory
System shows current stock levels.

FR-05: Demand Prediction
System predicts future stock needs using past data.

FR-06: Alerts
System sends low-stock alerts.

FR-07: Dashboard View
System displays stock insights visually.

Acceptance Criteria

Login must verify credentials

Stock updates reflect instantly

Predictions show estimated demand

Alerts trigger at threshold levels

These requirements define the core system behavior.
